Package grafioschtrader.gtnet.handler

Class GTNetMessageHandlerRegistry

java.lang.Object
grafioschtrader.gtnet.handler.GTNetMessageHandlerRegistry
@Component public class GTNetMessageHandlerRegistry extends Object
Registry that maps GTNet message codes to their handlers. Handlers are auto-discovered via Spring dependency injection. All beans implementing GTNetMessageHandler are automatically registered during construction.

Usage

 GTNetMessageHandler handler = registry.getHandler(messageCode);
 HandlerResult result = handler.handle(context);

  • Constructor Details

    • GTNetMessageHandlerRegistry

      public GTNetMessageHandlerRegistry(List<GTNetMessageHandler> handlerList)
      Creates the registry and registers all discovered handlers. Spring automatically injects all beans implementing GTNetMessageHandler. Each handler can support multiple message codes via GTNetMessageHandler.getSupportedMessageCodes().
      Parameters:
      handlerList - all GTNetMessageHandler beans in the application context
      Throws:
      IllegalStateException - if duplicate handlers are found for the same message code
